Class PSTouchParentItems

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.extension.PSDefaultExtension
      com.percussion.extensions.general.PSTouchParentItems
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSExtension, IPSWorkflowAction
public class PSTouchParentItems
extends PSDefaultExtension
implements IPSWorkflowAction

This workflow action touches all "active assembly parent" items of the current item. These items are found by searching the related content table for parent items, and then searching for the parents of those items, etc. The relationships are in the 'active assembly' category only.

The content items which are found are then updated so that the LastModifyDate column contains the current date & time.
